<TEXT>
a white supremacist accused in a lawsuit of inciting skinheads 
to commit a racially motivated killing in portland ore says he 
was merely exercising his first amendment rights 
the suit which seeks damages from the group white aryan 
resistance or war and four individuals is merely a roundabout 
way of cutting off freedom of speech freedom of association and 
even freedom of assembly said tom metzger the organizations 
leader and a defendant 
the oregon office of the american civil liberties union plans to 
monitor the trial set to begin monday in portland 
plaintiffs lawyer morris dees calls metzgers claims 
baloney 
the civil case follows the criminal conviction of three 
skinheads in the 1988 beating death of mulugeta seraw a 
27yearold ethiopian who was living and working in portland 
seraws skull was fractured with a baseball bat 
dees montgomery alabased southern poverty law center sued on 
behalf of seraws estate in the past the center has won millions 
in judgments by suing hate groups and their leaders arguing that 
they are responsible for damage and injuries done at their behest 
just as a corporation can be held liable for employees actions 
the suit contends metzger and his son john have recruited 
skinheads to war in recent years and that through agents they sent 
to portland they provided a skinhead group called east side white 
pride with racist materials promoting violence against blacks and 
jews seraws killers were members of east side white pride 
further the suit which was joined by the antidefamation 
league of bnai brith claims war agents were in contact with the 
metzgers in fallbrook calif met with the skinheads and 
encouraged them to harm blacks 
the allegations of personal involvement are totally 
nonsense metzger said its something that mr dees has 
dreamed up 
dees said he has letters and phone records linking the metzgers 
and their agents in portland as well as a damning 
affidavit in it one of the agents michael barrett tells of 
taking five baseball bats to portland of keeping close contact 
with the metzgers and of meeting with east side white pride 
skinheads 
we told them to use violence if they got an opportunity and 
to be sure and beat the hell out of the enemy barrett said in 
the affidavit we were telling them what tom and john metzger 
told us to say 
</TEXT>
